featured.text: Jessica is a very religious girl; she believes that she is always ______ supported by her god.

definition.zh_def: 一個常見的女性名字，源自希伯來語，意指「財富」或「上帝的恩賜」。
definition.en_def: A common female name of Hebrew origin meaning 'wealth' or 'God's gift.'
definition.example: Jessica is planning to travel to Europe next summer.
